





course1.htm


飛行力學
Flight Mechanics
開授年級:航太所學士班     
學分數:  3                                                                                                                       
選課類別:必修
課程簡介

This      
course deals with the dynamics of a fixed wing aircraft. In particular, we will do static      
analysis, as well as dynamic modeling, of aircraft motions. In the static analysis,      
criteria to ensure static longitudinal stability of an A/C will be addressed. In addition,      
discussions on the performance of several static lateral maneuvers will be included in      
static lateral motion analysis. In the dynamic analysis, linearized equations of motions      
derived from small perturbation approximation of aircraft motion are formulated. The link      
between the equation parameters and the aerodynamics of an aircraft will be addressed in      
detail. The characteristics of the linearized dynamic equations will then be analyzed      
using Laplace transform technique. Solutions to these linearized equations will represent      
the perturbed motion of the aircraft from an equilibrium flight condition. Finally,      
aircraft response to atmospheric disturbances will be discussed. The possible disastrous      
effect of microbursts on a near-ground and low energy aircraft will be examined.
課程大綱

A. Review of dynamics
B. Longitudinal motion analysis                                                                                                                       
     B.1 Static longitudinal analysis
          B.1.1                                                                                                                        
Static longitudinal stability
          B.1.2                                                                                                                        
Trim stabilizer & elevator angle for level flight
          B.1.3                                                                                                                        
Stick free static stability
          B.1.4                                                                                                                        
Maneuver point and maneuver margin
          B.1.5                                                                                                                        
Stick force for maneuver
     B.2 Dynamic longitudinal analysis
          B.2.1                                                                                                                        
Linearization of the longitudinal equations
          B.2.2                                                                                                                        
Estimation of longitudinal aerodynamic
                                                                                                                                           
derivatives
          B.2.3                                                                                                                        
Some preliminaries for longitudinal dynamic
                                                                                                                                           
analysis
          B.2.4                                                                                                                        
Characteristics of longitudinal dynamics (I)
                                                                                                                                           
--- Simplified longitudinal motions
          B.2.5                                                                                                                        
Characteristics of longitudinal dynamics (II)
                                                                                                                                           
--- Complete longitudinal motions
          B.2.6                                                                                                                        
Longitudinal response to control input
C. Lateral motion analysis                                                                                                                       
     C.1 Linearization of the lateral analysis
     C.2 Static lateral analysis
     C.3 Lateral dynamic equations
          C.3.1                                                                                                                        
Lateral directional derivatives
          C.3.2                                                                                                                        
  Aerodynamics of the lateral derivatives
     C.4 Dynamic lateral analysis
          C.4.1                                                                                                                        
Characteristics of lateral dynamics (I)
                                                                                                                                           
--- Some basic analysis
          C.4.2                                                                                                                        
Characteristics of lateral dynamics (II)
                                                                                                                                           
--- Effects of the varying parameters
          C.4.3                                                                                                                        
Lateral response to control input                                                                                                                       
D. A/C response to atmospheric gusts                                                                                                                       
     D.1 Rederive the longitudinal equations
     D.2 Longitudinal response to                                                                                                                        
vertical gusts
     D.3 Longitudinal response to                                                                                                                        
horizontal gusts

使用課本
Flight Stability and Automatic Control
 Nelson

